{"tid":1589084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"928, 929, 101 會唔會追加新口號？","createTime":"2019-09-23T06:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:31.000Z","uid":303750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf72b6b89a52cb9e31cd451619edc5492c60f43","tid":1589084,"uid":303750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"因為下星期行街主題<br />\n睇落唔只香港問題咁小兒科<br />\n而係全人類反對全球第二大經濟體<br />\n即係中共，帶頭搞極權玩暴力侵犯世界等等<br />\n甚至可能係香港呢場抗爭既新起點<br />\n所以希望大家一齊諗諗<br />\n除左會嗌舊口號<br />\n要唔要追加少少中英文新口號應一應景？<br />\n如果追加，新口號會反共到咩程度？<br />\n定係穩陣保持原狀，唔好俾位人入？"},{"pid":"74fdf3b9d9eb83070a9106632f1160a787d2cce5","tid":1589084,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"0f5c9692162e2574e16d478fc261d71a0e4c0b04","tid":1589084,"uid":203332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:17:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f6998a48f561326405b7b1d29ec7fc5bfcb65c0","tid":1589084,"uid":325882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d26987497b9bbd8f5c73c2d5955e33d34656994","tid":1589084,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"929幫埋新疆反赤納粹"},{"pid":"1f30de520001d3a9c0e11a8c2c310acad93f5eae","tid":1589084,"uid":303750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:54:51.000Z","msg":"聽鬼佬教授話要幫藍絲做文宣 airdrop<br />\n所以我試左下，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請廣傳！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/IsnDRy9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgu